Description:
    Generates a schedule.yml file for an event in an event series, auto-filling talk slots from videos.yml.
    Customize the generated file for multi-track events or special activities as needed.

Example:
    bin/rails generate schedule --event-series=SERIES_SLUG --event=EVENT_SLUG

    This will create:
        /data/SERIES_SLUG/EVENT_SLUG/schedule.yml
    The file will be pre-populated with a basic schedule template for editing.
